actionConfiguration.body:
INSERT IGNORE INTO ShippedLogs (Log, Docket, Length, Grade, ScaleDate, ShipDate, JAS, Diameter, Rego, Supplier, Operations, Coupe, Harvestor, FPP, Ordername, Vessel)
SELECT Log, Scaling.Docket, Scaling.Length, Scaling.Grade, Scaling.Date as ScaleDate, '{{new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]}}' as ShipDate, JAS, Diameter, Rego, Supplier, Operations, Coupe, Harvestor, FPP, Scaling.Ordername, Vessel FROM Scaling
JOIN
(SELECT Ordername, Vessel
		 FROM Orders
		 JOIN Shipment ON Orders.ShipmentID = Shipment.ShipmentID 
		 WHERE Orders.ShipmentID = {{SelectShipmentDispatch.selectedOptionValue}}) O
ON Scaling.Ordername = O.Ordername
JOIN 
WeighBridge ON WeighBridge.Docket = Scaling.Docket;
